          | Talent Acquisition will, from time to time, run “specials” for referral bonuses for hard to fill roles.  Bonuses will be paid after the completion of the new hire’s first 90 days. The referring employee as well as the referred employee must be employed at the time of the bonus payout in order to receive the payment.
          | Only one referral bonus can be given per candidate. If a candidate is referred by more than one employee, Talent Acquisition will decide who receives the referral bonus based on the date and time stamp of referral submission within Jobvite.
